11. **2026 outlook** — AI Overviews CPM trajectory, Prime Video scale, TikTok resolution, cookieless transition, retail media standardization, macro sensitivity\n\n**Data sourcing:** All Google and Amazon figures are confirmed from primary earnings releases. Meta capex ($115–135B) from semiconductor research. Meta ad revenue specifics, TTD figures noted as directional with caveat." ;
