# === finding-5225c445-22a5-468a-a01d-a4753cf20fe7 ===
<urn:tesserai:twin:finding-5225c445-22a5-468a-a01d-a4753cf20fe7> <http://tesserai.io/ontology/createdAt> "2026-03-27T17:15:00.97719Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> ;
