# === finding-5f56fbee-a2ea-4cd8-89ad-488cf09ddb1c ===
<urn:tesserai:twin:finding-5f56fbee-a2ea-4cd8-89ad-488cf09ddb1c> <http://tesserai.io/ontology/createdAt> "2026-03-27T17:22:28.729709Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> ;
