# === finding-d52d9a3a-8ddb-4d70-9392-f68ffd6ea6ba ===
<urn:tesserai:twin:finding-d52d9a3a-8ddb-4d70-9392-f68ffd6ea6ba> <http://tesserai.io/ontology/createdAt> "2026-03-27T17:11:10.49444Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> ;
	<http://tesserai.io/ontology/topics> "[\"Write Microsoft company summary\",\"coder\"]" ;
	<http://tesserai.io/ontology/run_id> "91ea36f6-9248-4f8f-a35c-65603e275bb8" ;
	<http://tesserai.io/ontology/memory_type> "semantic" ;
	<http://tesserai.io/ontology/created_at> "2026-03-27T17:11:10.494320+00:00" ;
	<http://tesserai.io/ontology/content> "I need permission to write the file. Please approve the file write to `/private/tmp/swarm-parallel-stocks/analysis/companies/microsoft.md`.\n\nThe summary I've prepared is based on research already captured in the project memory:\n\n**From cloud sector research:**\n- Intelligent Cloud: $32.9B (+29% YoY), ~43% operating margin\n- Azure: ~38–39% CC growth, gaining market share (20% → 21%)\n- Commercial cloud surpassed $50B milestone\n- AI described as \"larger than some established franchises\"\n- $120B+ 2026 capex\n\n**From semiconductor research:**\n- Microsoft Maia 200 announced Jan 2026 — 3x FP4 vs. Trainium3, better FP8 vs. Google TPU7\n- Azure Premium SSD prices raised 10–11%\n\n**Gap:** Total company revenue, EPS, and Productivity/MPC segment detail weren't captured by the research agents — the summary notes this explicitly and focuses on cloud/AI where data is complete." ;
	<http://tesserai.io/ontology/confidence> "0.8"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#double> ;
	<http://tesserai.io/ontology/agent_id> "328bc620-69d3-4159-b280-95d36ee267e5" ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "I need permission to write the file. Please approve the file write to `/private/tmp/swarm-parallel-stocks/analysis/companies/microsoft.md`.\n\nThe summary I've prepared is based on research already captured in the project memory:\n\n**From cloud sector research:**\n- Intelligent Cloud: $32.9B (+29% YoY), ~43% operating margin\n- Azure: ~38–39% CC growth, gaining market share (20% → 21%)\n- Commercial cloud surpassed $50B milestone\n- AI described as \"larger than some established franchises\"\n- $120B+ 2026 capex\n\n**From semiconductor research:**\n- Microsoft Maia 200 announced Jan 2026 — 3x FP4 vs. Trainium3, better FP8 vs. Google TPU7\n- Azure Premium SSD prices raised 10–11%\n\n**Gap:** Total company revenue, EPS, and Productivity/MPC segment detail weren't captured by the research agents — the summary notes this explicitly and focuses on cloud/AI where data is complete." ;
	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "I need permission to write the file. Please approve the file write to `/private/tmp/swarm-parallel-s" ;
