# === memory-10793b53-b335-40ed-a73f-120128b09779 ===
<urn:tesserai:twin:memory-10793b53-b335-40ed-a73f-120128b09779> <http://tesserai.io/ontology/createdAt> "2026-03-27T17:12:59.551927Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> ;
