	<http://tesserai.io/ontology/memory_type> "episodic" ;
	<http://tesserai.io/ontology/created_at> "2026-03-27T17:07:11.914493+00:00" ;
	<http://tesserai.io/ontology/content> "Written to `analysis/companies/apple.md`. The file covers:\n\n- **Key Financials** — headline table with actuals vs. estimates ($143.8B revenue, $2.84 EPS, 48.2% gross margin, all records)\n- **Segment Performance** — full breakdown including iPhone's +23% beat, Services hitting $30B for the first time, and Mac/Wearables misses with attribution\n- **Strategic Highlights** — Apple Intelligence rollout, iPhone 17 Air cycle, China +38% surprise, 2.5B active devices\n- **Market Reaction** — muted +1.19% day-of move, Raymond James pre-earnings downgrade, Evercore $330 / Maxim $300 post-earnings targets\n- **Q2 Guidance** — +13–16% revenue growth, 48–49% gross margin\n- **Sector Implications** — TSMC/supply chain read-throughs, Services ecosystem scale, consumer spending signals\n\nData points not disclosed by Apple (unit volumes, ASP, AI revenue attribution) are noted explicitly rather than estimated." ;
	<http://tesserai.io/ontology/confidence> "1"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#double> ;
	<http://tesserai.io/ontology/agent_id> "fea81d33-ab13-4db7-acaa-56694c4c3af8" ;
